{
  "$comment": "Conformance golden vectors for schemas/did-agent.schema.json. An implementation is conformant when it ACCEPTS every 'PASS' vector and REJECTS every 'FAIL' vector using that schema. Negative vectors encode the doctrine: soulbound=non-transferable, skill carries evidence_class, subject=agent only, zero PII, No Password Custody, well-formed DID.",
